---
title: Spring Tortelloni Gratin with Basil Pesto & Asparagus
description: This skillet pasta bake truly is a one-pot-wonder – even the creamy pesto sauce thickens in the pan while the tortellini cook! A crispy topping of panko and Parmesan goes under the boiler for a few minutes until bubbly, browned, and irresistible.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/54ff26ca6ced6eb4088b4580.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipecards/card/54ff26ca6ced6eb4088b4580.pdf
source: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipes/spring-tortelloni-gratin-54ff26ca6ced6eb4088b4580
course: main course
cuisine: Italian
time required: 25 minutes
nutrition:
  calories: 670 kcal
  fat: 28 g
  carbohydrates: 71 g
